#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.align.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.align"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:1 of
msgid "Align two objects on their axes with the specified join method."
msgstr "使用指定的连接方法在轴上对齐两个对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:3 of
msgid "Join method is specified for each axis Index."
msgstr "为每个轴 Index 指定连接方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:9 of
msgid "Align on index (0), columns (1), or both (None)."
msgstr "在索引 (0)、列 (1) 或两者 (None) 上对齐。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:11 of
msgid ""
"Broadcast across a level, matching Index values on the passed MultiIndex "
"level."
msgstr "在层级间广播，匹配传入的 MultiIndex 层级上的 Index 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:14 of
msgid ""
"Always returns new objects. If copy=False and no reindexing is required "
"then original objects are returned."
msgstr "总是返回新对象。如果 copy=False 且不需要重新索引，则返回原始对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:17 of
msgid ""
"Value to use for missing values. Defaults to NaN, but can be any "
"\"compatible\" value."
msgstr "用于缺失值的值。默认为 NaN，但可以是任何“兼容”的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:20 of
msgid ""
"Method to use for filling holes in reindexed Series:  - pad / ffill: "
"propagate last valid observation forward to next valid. - backfill / "
"bfill: use NEXT valid observation to fill gap."
msgstr ""
"用于填充重新索引 Series 中空洞的方法： - pad / ffill: 将上一个有效观测值"
"向前传播到下一个有效值。 - backfill / bfill: 使用下一个有效观测值填充空缺"
"。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:20 of
msgid "Method to use for filling holes in reindexed Series:"
msgstr "用于填充重新索引的 Series 中空洞的方法："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:22 of
msgid "pad / ffill: propagate last valid observation forward to next valid."
msgstr "pad / ffill：将最后一个有效观测值向前传播到下一个有效值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:23 of
msgid "backfill / bfill: use NEXT valid observation to fill gap."
msgstr "backfill / bfill：使用下一个有效观测值填充空缺。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:25 of
msgid ""
"If method is specified, this is the maximum number of consecutive NaN "
"values to forward/backward fill. In other words, if there is a gap with "
"more than this number of consecutive NaNs, it will only be partially "
"filled. If method is not specified, this is the maximum number of entries"
" along the entire axis where NaNs will be filled. Must be greater than 0 "
"if not None."
msgstr ""
"如果指定了方法，这是向前/向后填充连续 NaN 值的最大数量。换句话说，如果"
"存在超过此数量连续 NaN 的间隙，则只会部分填充。如果未指定方法，则这是沿"
"整个轴填充 NaN 的最大条目数。如果不为 None，则必须大于 0。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:32 of
msgid "Filling axis, method and limit."
msgstr "填充轴、方法和限制。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:34 of
msgid ""
"Broadcast values along this axis, if aligning two objects of different "
"dimensions."
msgstr "如果对齐两个不同维度的对象，则沿此轴广播值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:39 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:40 of
msgid "Currently argument `level` is not supported."
msgstr "目前不支持参数 `level`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:42 of
msgid "**(left, right)** -- Aligned objects."
msgstr "**(left, right)** -- 对齐的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

