msgid "Align on columns:"
msgstr "按列对齐："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:80 of
msgid "We can also align on the index:"
msgstr "我们也可以按索引对齐："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.align.align:96 of
msgid "Finally, the default `axis=None` will align on both index and columns:"
msgstr "最后，默认的 `axis=None` 将在索引和列上都对齐："

